cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper discusses machine learning algorithms and metric learning, which are topics commonly found in the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of metrics in comparing individuals is also relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper proposes a method for improving accuracy and scalability, which is a common concern in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
